N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1ยง 6.6 - Posting license

State Regulations
A licensee shall keep his license or a copy thereof at his
place of employment and such license shall be posted conspicuously, except a
person who holds a milk receiver's license and who picks up milk from dairy
farms shall carry his milk receiver's license with him or in his bulk milk
pick-up truck. Notes
